name: BARK006
description:
"the dynamics of the dream world match the dynamics of the real world to a certain degree of resolution"

BARK is a digital series comprised of 7 OBJKT. 
Pictures of wood bark are heavily processed to create a dream like canvas and let the viewer's consciousness rebuild their own reality.

New OBJKT will be minted daily at 20:00 CET until 10/09/2021.
